cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.NE 

This paper combines methods from cognitive science and natural language processing to predict emotions. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which focuses on natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper explores the representational space of emotions, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
